     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"All these patches are fine I guess, but they haven't taken away this empty feeling inside."</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
